Battleship Requirements 
- Needs Grid = x and y at least 10 
- Needs ships of different length 
- needs technique for record a hit on a given ship 
- needs the abititly to play by two players 
- Needs classifcation of ships 
- needs ways to record misses 
- needs way to place ships on grid 
- needs way to use record of hits to count ships sunk
  needs to be able to check if ships sunk for win condition 
- keep tally of win and losses in record 
